    <briefdescription>
<para>A scheduler for events. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Stores events until a given time and add them to the event driver.<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>thread-safe.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>limited to a maximum of 10&apos;000 scheduled events. If more events are added, they are discarded.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>limited to a scheduling time of 0-12h. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
